Description

This task covers the completion of PLDM (Product & Lineage Data Management) assessments for all January intake Jira tickets related to TechADS DQ Controls and PARCM processes.

The assessment includes reviewing metadata impacts, validating ADS / ADST / AIT changes, and coordinating with relevant domain and development teams to ensure all PLDM requirements are satisfied prior to closure.

The goal is to ensure that all intake tickets are properly assessed, documented, and either approved or routed for follow-up remediation in alignment with governance and audit expectations.

